@bhrenton I didn’t know “success” actually meant “abysmal failure”. You learn something new every day.

@bhrenton No human interventions have been successful to any degree. The vaccines have failed, and there are no viable treatments. Everything that government has done has been all pain and no gain. Letting it rip from the beginning with zero restrictions was the only thing that made sense.
@bhrenton Wow, 7 day avgs for daily cases have exceeded 100,000/day for all but a handful of days since last August.

@bhrenton “…to help us build on the successes over the last 13 months…” Successes? Well, COVID certainly had a lot of successes, about half a million or so dead Americans and millions more debilitated with long COVID. Biden’s strategy was an utter disaster. Stop gaslighting people.

@bhrenton Every time Biden manipulates the data so he can try to justify telling people to stop wearing masks way too early, it just means more people assume masks don't work and resist wearing them when a new variant emerges.
